Oops!  Tally the entire matrix, not just the upper triangular portion.
Adding the code in red (4th line from top) should rectify the error.

for(i in 1:(nrow(x)-1)){
    for(j in (i+1):nrow(x)){
      mat[i,j] <- x$min[j] <= x$max[i]
      *mat[j,i] <- mat[i,j]*
    }
}






